dct_title_s: Gloucester City, including Highland Park and part of Center Township, Camden County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: "Jany. 1923." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. "5719". Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-20 of Gloucester City series; sheets 21-23, showing Highland Park and Center Township, foldered separately.
